ription><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3251272/chinese-security-agencies-tell-students-studying-abroad-beware-risk-foreign-spies?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国任命新监管负责人，警惕股市低迷</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251281/china-wary-stock-market-downturn-appoints-new-regulatory-chief?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着中国制定措施控制市场，拥有上海证券交易所经验的吴庆被任命为中国证券监管机构的负责人。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:17:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3251281/china-wary-stock-market-downturn-appoints-new-regulatory-chief?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>北京警告美日军演之际“阻碍中国统一”将付出“沉重代价”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251276/beijing-warns-heavy-price-obstructing-chinas-reunification-us-and-japan-stage-military-drills?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>日本媒体报道今年的“利刃”演习将台湾与北京的冲突嘲笑为“假想的敌人”后，中国大陆驻东京代表团发布了这一信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251276/beijing-warns-heavy-price-obstructing-chinas-reunification-us-and-japan-stage-military-drills?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中韩关系：朝鲜、俄罗斯、美国、日本阴影笼罩中韩关系</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251239/china-south-korea-relations-last-foreign-ministers-talk-shadow-north-korea-russia-us-japan-loom-over?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在王毅和赵太烈之间的第一次通话中，北京誓言将维护对韩政策的“稳定性和连续性”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251239/china-south-korea-relations-last-foreign-ministers-talk-shadow-north-korea-russia-us-japan-loom-over?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>抖音CEO张凯莉辞去TikTok中文版负责人职务，专注于字节跳动视频编辑CapCut和AI</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/32